{
  "easy": {
    "title": "Refactor Non-Semantic HTML to Clean Code",
    "description": "The following HTML is a 'div soup' with inconsistent formatting, inline styles, and inline event handlers. Refactor it to use semantic elements, consistent indentation, BEM naming, proper separation of concerns, and data attributes.",
    "starterCode": "<div class='wrapper' style='max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;padding:20px;'>\n<div class='header' style='background:#333;color:white;padding:20px;text-align:center;'>\n<h1>My App</h1>\n<div class='nav'><a href='#' style='color:white;margin:0 10px;'>Home</a><a href='#' style='color:white;margin:0 10px;'>About</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class='content'>\n  <div class='post'>\n  <h2>Post Title</h2>\n  <p>Post content here</p>\n  <button onclick=\"alert('liked')\" style='background:blue;color:white;padding:10px;border:none;border-radius:4px;'>\n  Like\n  </button>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class='footer' style='background:#333;color:white;text-align:center;padding:10px;'>&copy; 2026</div>\n</div>",
    "solution": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <title>My App</title>\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"styles.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"app\">\n    <header class=\"header\">\n      <h1 class=\"header__title\">My App</h1>\n      <nav class=\"nav\" aria-label=\"Main\">\n        <a href=\"/\" class=\"nav__link\">Home</a>\n        <a href=\"/about\" class=\"nav__link\">About</a>\n      </nav>\n    </header>\n    \n    <main class=\"main\">\n      <article class=\"post\">\n        <h2 class=\"post__title\">Post Title</h2>\n        <p class=\"post__content\">Post content here</p>\n        <button class=\"btn btn--like\" data-action=\"like\">\n          Like\n        </button>\n      </article>\n    </main>\n    \n    <footer class=\"footer\">\n      <p class=\"footer__text\">&copy; 2026</p>\n    </footer>\n  </div>\n  \n  <script src=\"app.js\" defer></script>\n</body>\n</html>\n\n<!-- Separate CSS file (styles.css): -->\n<!--\n.app { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }\n.header { background: #333; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }\n.header__title { margin: 0 0 10px; }\n.nav__link { color: white; margin: 0 10px; text-decoration: none; }\n.main { padding: 20px 0; }\n.post { margin-bottom: 30px; }\n.btn { padding: 10px 20px; border: none; border-radius: 4px; cursor: pointer; }\n.btn--like { background: #3498db; color: white; }\n.btn--like:hover { background: #2980b9; }\n.footer { background: #333; color: white; text-align: center; padding: 10px; }\n-->\n\n<!-- Separate JS file (app.js): -->\n<!--\ndocument.querySelector('[data-action=\"like\"]')\n  .addEventListener('click', () => alert('liked'));\n-->"
  },
  "medium": {
    "title": "Implement BEM Component Library",
    "description": "Create a reusable card component library using BEM naming. The card component should support: default card, card with image, card with header/footer, card with primary action button, card in featured modifier, and card in horizontal layout modifier. Write the HTML for each variant and show how the BEM naming makes the component relationships clear.",
    "starterCode": "<!-- Create a card component system using BEM -->\n<!-- Include these variants: -->\n<!-- 1. Default card: .card -->\n<!-- 2. Card with image: .card.card--with-image -->\n<!-- 3. Featured card: .card.card--featured -->\n<!-- 4. Horizontal card: .card.card--horizontal -->\n<!-- Elements: card__image, card__header, card__body, card__title, card__text, card__footer, card__button -->\n\n<div class=\"card\">\n  <!-- Default card -->\n</div>",
    "solution": "<!-- Card Component Library -->\n\n<!-- 1. Default Card -->\n<article class=\"card\">\n  <div class=\"card__body\">\n    <h3 class=\"card__title\">Default Card</h3>\n    <p class=\"card__text\">This is a basic card with no image, just title and content.</p>\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- 2. Card with Image -->\n<article class=\"card card--with-image\">\n  <img class=\"card__image\" src=\"photo.jpg\" alt=\"Card image\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  <div class=\"card__body\">\n    <h3 class=\"card__title\">Image Card</h3>\n    <p class=\"card__text\">This card includes an image element above the content.</p>\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- 3. Card with Header and Footer -->\n<article class=\"card\">\n  <header class=\"card__header\">\n    <h3 class=\"card__title\">Full Card</h3>\n  </header>\n  <div class=\"card__body\">\n    <p class=\"card__text\">This card has header, body, and footer sections with a call-to-action button.</p>\n  </div>\n  <footer class=\"card__footer\">\n    <a href=\"#\" class=\"card__button card__button--primary\">Learn More</a>\n  </footer>\n</article>\n\n<!-- 4. Featured Card (Modifier) -->\n<article class=\"card card--featured\">\n  <div class=\"card__header\">\n    <h3 class=\"card__title\">Featured Card</h3>\n    <span class=\"card__badge\">Featured</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"card__body\">\n    <p class=\"card__text\">This card uses the --featured modifier for emphasis with a border highlight.</p>\n  </div>\n  <footer class=\"card__footer\">\n    <a href=\"#\" class=\"card__button card__button--primary\">Get Started</a>\n  </footer>\n</article>\n\n<!-- 5. Horizontal Card (Modifier) -->\n<article class=\"card card--horizontal\">\n  <img class=\"card__image\" src=\"photo.jpg\" alt=\"Horizontal layout\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  <div class=\"card__body\">\n    <h3 class=\"card__title\">Horizontal Card</h3>\n    <p class=\"card__text\">This card uses the --horizontal modifier for a side-by-side layout with the image next to the content.</p>\n    <a href=\"#\" class=\"card__button card__button--secondary\">Details</a>\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- CSS Structure (ideas):\n.card { border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; }\n.card--featured { border-color: gold; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255,215,0,0.3); }\n.card--horizontal { display: flex; }\n.card--with-image { padding: 0; }\n.card__image { width: 100%; display: block; }\n.card__header { padding: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }\n.card__body { padding: 15px; }\n.card__title { margin: 0 0 10px; }\n.card__text { color: #666; }\n.card__footer { padding: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; }\n.card__button { padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; }\n.card__button--primary { background: #3498db; color: white; }\n.card__button--secondary { background: #95a5a6; color: white; }\n.card__badge { background: gold; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.8em; }\n-->"
  },
  "hard": {
    "title": "Create a Complete Design System Component Page with Clean Code Standards",
    "description": "Build a design system documentation page that showcases HTML components with perfect clean code standards. The page must include: a header with navigation, a sidebar with component categories, a main area showing components (buttons, cards, forms, navigation, alerts) with code previews, and a footer. Requirements: BEM naming throughout, EditorConfig configuration, proper commenting strategy, HTMLHint-compliant code, semantic elements, data attributes for JS, proper heading hierarchy, accessibility attributes, and separation of concerns (external CSS/JS only). The HTML must be production-quality and pass validation.",
    "starterCode": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n  <title>Design System</title>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <!-- Build a complete design system documentation page -->\n</body>\n</html>",
    "solution": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <title>Design System - Web Components</title>\n  <meta name=\"description\" content=\"A clean, accessible design system documentation page.\">\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"design-system.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n<!-- ==========================================\n     SKIP LINK\n     ========================================== -->\n<a href=\"#main-content\" class=\"skip-link\">Skip to main content</a>\n\n<!-- ==========================================\n     HEADER\n     ========================================== -->\n<header class=\"header\">\n  <a href=\"/\" class=\"header__logo\" aria-label=\"Design System Home\">\n    <img src=\"logo.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"header__logo-img\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\">\n    <span class=\"header__logo-text\">Design System</span>\n  </a>\n  <nav class=\"nav\" aria-label=\"Main\">\n    <button class=\"nav__toggle\" data-action=\"toggle-nav\" aria-controls=\"nav-list\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\n      <span class=\"sr-only\">Menu</span>\n    </button>\n    <ul id=\"nav-list\" class=\"nav__list\" data-visible=\"false\">\n      <li class=\"nav__item\"><a href=\"/\" class=\"nav__link nav__link--active\" aria-current=\"page\">Home</a></li>\n      <li class=\"nav__item\"><a href=\"/components\" class=\"nav__link\">Components</a></li>\n      <li class=\"nav__item\"><a href=\"/patterns\" class=\"nav__link\">Patterns</a></li>\n      <li class=\"nav__item\"><a href=\"/tokens\" class=\"nav__link\">Design Tokens</a></li>\n    </ul>\n  </nav>\n</header>\n<!-- /HEADER -->\n\n<!-- ==========================================\n     LAYOUT\n     ========================================== -->\n<div class=\"layout\">\n  \n  <!-- Sidebar -->\n  <aside class=\"sidebar\" aria-label=\"Component categories\">\n    <nav class=\"sidebar__nav\" aria-label=\"Components\">\n      <h2 class=\"sidebar__title\">Components</h2>\n      <ul class=\"sidebar__list\">\n        <li class=\"sidebar__item\"><a href=\"#buttons\" class=\"sidebar__link sidebar__link--active\">Buttons</a></li>\n        <li class=\"sidebar__item\"><a href=\"#cards\" class=\"sidebar__link\">Cards</a></li>\n        <li class=\"sidebar__item\"><a href=\"#forms\" class=\"sidebar__link\">Forms</a></li>\n        <li class=\"sidebar__item\"><a href=\"#navigation\" class=\"sidebar__link\">Navigation</a></li>\n        <li class=\"sidebar__item\"><a href=\"#alerts\" class=\"sidebar__link\">Alerts</a></li>\n      </ul>\n    </nav>\n  </aside>\n\n  <!-- ==========================================\n       MAIN CONTENT\n       ========================================== -->\n  <main id=\"main-content\" class=\"main\">\n    \n    <h1 class=\"main__title\">Component Library</h1>\n    <p class=\"main__description\">A clean, accessible collection of UI components following BEM naming and WCAG standards.</p>\n\n    <!-- Buttons Section -->\n    <section id=\"buttons\" class=\"component-section\">\n      <h2 class=\"component-section__title\">Buttons</h2>\n      \n      <article class=\"component-preview\">\n        <h3 class=\"component-preview__title\">Button Variants</h3>\n        <div class=\"component-preview__demo\">\n          <button class=\"btn btn--primary\" type=\"button\">Primary</button>\n          <button class=\"btn btn--secondary\" type=\"button\">Secondary</button>\n          <button class=\"btn btn--outline\" type=\"button\">Outline</button>\n          <button class=\"btn btn--danger\" type=\"button\">Danger</button>\n          <button class=\"btn btn--primary\" type=\"button\" disabled>Disabled</button>\n        </div>\n        <pre class=\"component-preview__code\">\n&lt;button class=\"btn btn--primary\"&gt;Primary&lt;/button&gt;\n&lt;button class=\"btn btn--secondary\"&gt;Secondary&lt;/button&gt;\n&lt;button class=\"btn btn--outline\"&gt;Outline&lt;/button&gt;\n&lt;button class=\"btn btn--danger\"&gt;Danger&lt;/button&gt;\n&lt;button class=\"btn btn--primary\" disabled&gt;Disabled&lt;/button&gt;</pre>\n      </article>\n\n      <article class=\"component-preview\">\n        <h3 class=\"component-preview__title\">Button Sizes</h3>\n        <div class=\"component-preview__demo\">\n          <button class=\"btn btn--primary btn--sm\" type=\"button\">Small</button>\n          <button class=\"btn btn--primary\" type=\"button\">Default</button>\n          <button class=\"btn btn--primary btn--lg\" type=\"button\">Large</button>\n        </div>\n        <pre class=\"component-preview__code\">\n&lt;button class=\"btn btn--primary btn--sm\"&gt;Small&lt;/button&gt;\n&lt;button class=\"btn btn--primary\"&gt;Default&lt;/button&gt;\n&lt;button class=\"btn btn--primary btn--lg\"&gt;Large&lt;/button&gt;</pre>\n      </article>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- Cards Section -->\n    <section id=\"cards\" class=\"component-section\">\n      <h2 class=\"component-section__title\">Cards</h2>\n      \n      <div class=\"card-grid\">\n        <article class=\"card\">\n          <div class=\"card__body\">\n            <h3 class=\"card__title\">Simple Card</h3>\n            <p class=\"card__text\">A basic card component with title and body text.</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"card__footer\">\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"card__link\">Read more</a>\n          </div>\n        </article>\n        \n        <article class=\"card card--featured\">\n          <div class=\"card__header\">\n            <h3 class=\"card__title\">Featured Card</h3>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"card__body\">\n            <p class=\"card__text\">A featured card with highlighted border and header.</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"card__footer\">\n            <button class=\"btn btn--primary\" type=\"button\">Get Started</button>\n          </div>\n        </article>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- Forms Section -->\n    <section id=\"forms\" class=\"component-section\">\n      <h2 class=\"component-section__title\">Forms</h2>\n      \n      <form class=\"form\" novalidate>\n        <fieldset class=\"form__fieldset\">\n          <legend class=\"form__legend\">User Information</legend>\n          \n          <div class=\"form__group\">\n            <label for=\"full-name\" class=\"form__label\">Full Name</label>\n            <input type=\"text\" id=\"full-name\" class=\"form__input\" name=\"fullName\" required aria-required=\"true\" autocomplete=\"name\">\n            <span class=\"form__error\" role=\"alert\" aria-describedby=\"full-name\"></span>\n          </div>\n          \n          <div class=\"form__group\">\n            <label for=\"user-email\" class=\"form__label\">Email</label>\n            <input type=\"email\" id=\"user-email\" class=\"form__input\" name=\"email\" required aria-required=\"true\" autocomplete=\"email\">\n            <span class=\"form__error\" role=\"alert\"></span>\n          </div>\n          \n          <div class=\"form__group\">\n            <label for=\"user-bio\" class=\"form__label\">Biography</label>\n            <textarea id=\"user-bio\" class=\"form__textarea\" name=\"bio\" rows=\"3\"></textarea>\n          </div>\n          \n          <div class=\"form__actions\">\n            <button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn btn--primary\">Submit</button>\n            <button type=\"reset\" class=\"btn btn--outline\">Reset</button>\n          </div>\n        </fieldset>\n      </form>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- Alerts Section -->\n    <section id=\"alerts\" class=\"component-section\">\n      <h2 class=\"component-section__title\">Alerts</h2>\n      \n      <div class=\"alert alert--info\" role=\"alert\">\n        <p class=\"alert__text\">This is an informational alert message.</p>\n        <button class=\"alert__close\" data-action=\"close-alert\" aria-label=\"Close\">&times;</button>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"alert alert--success\" role=\"alert\">\n        <p class=\"alert__text\">Your changes have been saved successfully.</p>\n        <button class=\"alert__close\" data-action=\"close-alert\" aria-label=\"Close\">&times;</button>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"alert alert--warning\" role=\"alert\">\n        <p class=\"alert__text\">Please review your input before submitting.</p>\n        <button class=\"alert__close\" data-action=\"close-alert\" aria-label=\"Close\">&times;</button>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"alert alert--error\" role=\"alert\">\n        <p class=\"alert__text\">An error occurred while processing your request.</p>\n        <button class=\"alert__close\" data-action=\"close-alert\" aria-label=\"Close\">&times;</button>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n  </main>\n</div>\n\n<!-- ==========================================\n     FOOTER\n     ========================================== -->\n<footer class=\"footer\">\n  <p class=\"footer__text\">&copy; 2026 Design System. Built with clean code standards.</p>\n  <nav class=\"footer__nav\" aria-label=\"Footer\">\n    <a href=\"/privacy\" class=\"footer__link\">Privacy</a>\n    <a href=\"/accessibility\" class=\"footer__link\">Accessibility</a>\n    <a href=\"/github\" class=\"footer__link\">GitHub</a>\n  </nav>\n</footer>\n<!-- /FOOTER -->\n\n<script src=\"design-system.js\" defer></script>\n</body>\n</html>"
  }
}